53	        "     second in the future, with a sample rate of 1 MSps and constant\n"
54	        "     baseband data with I and Q component having a value of 0.5:\n"
55	        "       tx_bursts --args=\"addr=192.168.10.2\" --freq=2.4e9 --rate=1e6\n"
