57	        "  2. Repeated transmission of bursts of 10,000 samples at 2.4 GHz,\n"
58	        "     starting 1 second in the future, with a sample rate of 1 MSps. Each\n"
59	        "     burst is repeated every 0.5 seconds until interrupted:\n"
60	        "       tx_bursts --args=\"addr=192.168.10.2\" --freq=2.4e9 --rate=1e6\n"
